239
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,970
Objection.

240
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,450
Votre Honneur, la prévenue est clairement...

241
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:03,050
Votre Honneur, Mrs. Darling n'a pas d'antécedents...

242
00:11:03,070 --> 00:11:06,330
